data.description: SHOWINGS BEGIN 2/10/24! Welcome to this stunning Mason home ideally situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering easy access to I-71. Nestled in a sought-after pool community with a clubhouse, this residence boasts a beautiful yard complete with a spacious paver patio and basketball hoop, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. Inside, the master suite features vaulted ceilings and double vanities, adding to the allure of this property. With an attached two-car garage and ample entertainment space throughout, this home presents a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.
